Maintainer: Samir Rachid Zaim <samir.rachidzaim@alleninstitute.org>
Description: scMACS is a novel peak-calling algorithm that captures and leverage single-cell 
             information to model and identify accesible chromatin in single-cell 
             ATAC-Sequencing data.
